  Inline SVG, stroke inherits from the <svg> element (stroke=currentColor), so icons
  take the colour of their text context. Sized via CSS (.ico) or the optional `size` arg.

  Usage:
    {% from "icons.html.j2" import icon %}
    {{ icon('grid') }}
    {{ icon('power', cls='ico', size=16) }}
